high_descs: walk to the right in the kitchen to face the counter to the right of the stove
pick up the green lettuce on the right side from the counter
walk to the right to face the fridge
open the fridge door, place the lettuce in the fridge shelf, close the door, wait for lettuce to chill, open the fridge door, pick up the lettuce and close the door
walk left to face the sink and counter to the left of the sink
place the lettuce on the counter top to the left of the sink
anns.task_desc: put a chilled lettuce on a kitchen counter

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the heads of lettuce on the counter.
Pick up the closest head of lettuce on the right.
Turn around and walk to the refrigerator.
Put the head of lettuce in the refrigerator for a few seconds, take it out and close the refrigerator.
Turn left and walk to the counter to the left of the sink.
Put the head of lettuce on the counter, to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooled head of lettuce on a counter top.

high_descs: Go right and face the counter with all the lettuce on it.
Pick the lettuce on the right up from the counter.
Turn around and go straight and then turn to the left to face the fridge.
Put the lettuce in the fridge and shut the door and then open the door and pick the lettuce back up again.
Go left and then turn to face the sink.
Put the lettuce on the counter to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled head of lettuce on the counter.
